  • Method Details

    • markAsObfuscated

      void markAsObfuscated()
      Mark an entity as obfuscated. For EffDated entitites just mark this slice. Calling this method on an obfuscated entity has no effect. Once marked as obfuscated, an entity cannot later be "unmarked".

    • isObfuscated

      boolean isObfuscated()
      Whether or not the associated Obfuscatable has been obfuscated.
      Returns:
      true if marked as obfuscated, false else
